These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, soccer
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, white
1. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Sport           | soccer | golf |
| Color   | white     | chestnut  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, coach
1. the dancer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing   | drawing      |
| Job   | dancer | coach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, yellow
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, thriller
1. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Color   | yellow | blood-red    |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts | thriller |

 #################################

 
