.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, june
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, entrepreneur
1. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
2. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Birthday   | june | february |
| Job     | entrepreneur   | lawyer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-11::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage           | juice  | coffee  |
| Cigar   | swisher | dannemann |

